This paper is about image attribute editing, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper proposes a new method that incorporates encoder-decoder and generative adversarial networks for attribute editing, which suggests that it could also fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions season translation, which could suggest that it falls under graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
